Item 8.01. Other Events.
On August 8, 2006, Albemarle Corporation (the "Company") issued a press release announcing that it had signed a letter of intent with International Chemical Investors Group ("ICIG") with respect to the possible transfer of the Company's facility in Thann, France, to ICIG. A copy of the press release issued by the Company on August 8, 2006 is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 and incorporated herein by reference.
Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits.
 
 
