Set forth on is a complete and accurate list as of the Closing Date of each Subsidiary of the Company, together with (i) the jurisdiction of formation, (ii) an indication of whether such Subsidiary is a Material Domestic Subsidiary, and (iii) the ownership percentage of the Company or any Subsidiary therein.
