On April 23, 2007, Albemarle Corporation (the "Company") issued a press release regarding its earnings for the first quarter ended March 31, 2007. A copy of this release is being furnished as Exhibit 99.1 hereto and incorporated herein by reference. In addition, on April 24, 2007, the Company will hold a teleconference for analysts and media to discuss results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2007. The teleconference will be webcast on the Company's website at .
