Upon Mr. Allens departure, Scott Tozier, Senior Vice President, Chief Financial Officer and Chief Risk Officer of the Company, will assume the duties of principal accounting officer.  Mr. Tozier will perform these duties in addition to his current duties as principal financial officer.
 
 
 
 
